Board RAM (KBC).code:
; NAME: Board RAM (KBC)
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct

ADDIU SP SP -4
SW RA 0(SP)

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex
NOP

LW RA 0(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 4

